These are Puzzles for 1x6 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-1-1::.
6 different games are played: poker, monopoly, mah-jongg, whist, scrabble, canasta
1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far right##1
2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing whist##1
3. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
4. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing poker##1
5. the person playing monopoly is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |       2        |     3     |      4       |   5   |   6    |
| Game   | monopoly | scrabble | poker | canasta | whist | mah-jongg |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-1-2::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  project-manager, chef, entrepreneur, mechanic, librarian, accountant
1. the entrepreneur is on the right of the project-manager##1
2. the mechanic is on the far left##1
3. the librarian is on the left of the chef##1
4. the entrepreneur is on the left of the accountant##1
5. the project-manager is on the right of the mechanic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |   5    |    6    |
| Job   | mechanic | project-manager | entrepreneur | accountant | librarian | chef |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-1-3::.
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: dahlia, daisy, tulip, daffodil, amaryllis, iris
1. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
2. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
3. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
4. the person who growsdaisy is on the far left##1
5. the person who growsdaffodil is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |   3    |    4     |       5       |       6       |
| Flower   | daisy | tulip | amaryllis | dahlia | iris | daffodil |

