.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-1-4::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: light-blue, blood-red, coral, lavender, amber, emerald
1. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
2. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
3. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
4. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
5. the person who likes coral is on the far left##1
6. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |   3    |    4    |      5      |  6  |
| Color   | coral | light-blue | emerald | blood-red | amber | lavender |

