1. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
2. the person watching family movies is on the far right##1
3. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
4. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
5. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |   5    |  6  |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | action | scientific | western | sports | family |

