3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
5. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
6. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |    3    |    4     |   5    |     6     |
| Pet   | hedgehog | horse | rabbit | hamster | mouse | guinea-pig |

