2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far right##1
6. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2       |      3      |     4     |   5    |     6     |
| Birthday   | october | september | may | august | february | april |

