2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person playing poker##1
3. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person playing domino##1
4. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
5. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing go##1
6. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |  3   |    4    |     5      |   6   |
| Game   | bridge | billiard | domino | mah-jongg | poker | go |

