.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-1-20::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: bus, taxi, jet-ski, bike, snowmobile, van
1. the person driving the bike is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the van##1
5. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
6. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3    |     4      |      5      |   6   |
| Transport   | bus | jet-ski | van | snowmobile | taxi | bike |

 